title: Petition/Application Was Rejected For Insufficient Funds
body: On April 21, 2021, we rejected your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190133848 because your filing fee was returned by your financial institution for insufficient funds. Any previously assigned priority or processing date is no longer applicable. If you wish to still pursue the benefit, you must file a new application or petition and submit a new fee filing fee. If you need assistance, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you change your mailing address, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
